############### OpenRouter Modes ###############
# If you want to use a specific model, copy one of the lines below and put it in the OPENROUTER_MODEL= of your .env file.
# If not set, it will default to "OPENROUTER_MODEL=mistralai/mistral-small-3.2-24b-instruct:free"
# You can also set it to any model available on OpenRouter: https://openrouter.ai/models
# Additional free models commonly available on OpenRouter : 

baidu/qianfan-ocr-fast:free                  # Categories: OCR, Vision, Data Extraction. Description: Domain-specific multimodal model purpose-built for fast and accurate Optical Character Recognition (OCR).
google/gemma-3-12b-it:free                   # Categories: General NLP, Logic, Assistant. Description: Mid-sized multimodal model handling up to 128k tokens, offering solid math, reasoning, and function calling.
google/gemma-3-27b-it:free                   # Categories: Logic, General NLP, Roleplay. Description: The largest Gemma 3 open model, delivering advanced math, reasoning, and chat capabilities.
google/gemma-3-4b-it:free                    # Categories: Edge Computing, Automation. Description: Lightweight Gemma 3 model designed for rapid, low-latency text generation and basic reasoning tasks.
google/gemma-3n-e2b-it:free                  # Categories: Mobile, Edge Computing. Description: Ultra-lightweight MatFormer architecture model optimized for low-resource environments and on-device execution.
google/gemma-3n-e4b-it:free                  # Categories: Mobile, Edge Computing. Description: Efficient 4B model optimized for privacy-focused, offline-capable applications and mobile processing.
google/gemma-4-26b-a4b-it:free               # Categories: Agents, Logic, General NLP. Description: Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) model delivering high-quality reasoning and native function calling at a fraction of compute cost.
google/gemma-4-31b-it:free                   # Categories: Complex Reasoning, Math, Code. Description: Dense multimodal model featuring a 256K context window, configurable thinking mode, and strong document understanding.
inclusionai/ling-2.6-1t:free                 # Categories: Finance, Code, Roleplay, Agents. Description: Trillion-parameter flagship instruct model using "fast thinking" for high efficiency in large-scale agent workflows.
liquid/lfm-2.5-1.2b-instruct:free            # Categories: Edge Computing, Chat. Description: Compact 1.2B instruction-tuned model built for fast on-device AI and strong conversational quality.
liquid/lfm-2.5-1.2b-thinking:free            # Categories: Logic, Agents. Description: Lightweight reasoning-focused model optimized for agentic tasks, data extraction, and RAG on edge devices.
meta-llama/llama-3.2-3b-instruct:free        # Categories: Mobile, Dialogue, General NLP. Description: Multilingual 3B model optimized for on-device natural language processing, summarization, and instruction-following.
meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct:free       # Categories: Code, Math, Logic, Dialogue. Description: Highly capable 70B model optimized for multilingual dialogue, complex logic, and deep reasoning tasks.
