nousresearch/hermes-3-405b-instruct:free     # Categories: Uncensored, Roleplay, Agents. Description: Frontier-level 405B model focused on user alignment, powerful steering, and unrestricted roleplay/agentic workflows.
nvidia/llama-nemotron-embed-vl-1b-v2:free    # Categories: Embeddings, Vision, Retrieval. Description: Vision-Language embedding model optimized for multimodal question-answering retrieval and document processing.
nvidia/nemotron-3-nano-30b-a3b:free          # Categories: Agents, Logic, Automation. Description: Highly efficient small MoE model designed for building specialized, privacy-focused agentic AI systems.
nvidia/nemotron-3-nano-omni:free             # Categories: Multimodal, Agents, Video. Description: Perception and context sub-agent processing text, image, video, and audio inputs in a single inference loop.
nvidia/nemotron-3-super:free                 # Categories: Agents, Complex Reasoning. Description: 120B open hybrid MoE model with a 1M token context, excelling at multi-step task planning and coherence.
nvidia/nemotron-nano-12b-2-vl:free           # Categories: Vision, OCR, Document Analysis. Description: Multimodal reasoning model designed for high-fidelity video understanding, chart reasoning, and OCR.
nvidia/nemotron-nano-9b-v2:free              # Categories: General NLP, Logic. Description: Unified reasoning model that can dynamically generate internal thought traces before answering user queries.
